body:
### FAQ:
* Why are you canceling live streams?
We aren't! We are moving them to a new channel called BobPony+.
* What about BobPony+?
It's a new channel that we will be putting the live streams on.
* Why will it cost money?
We need a way to make better quality episodes, and this is the best way to do it so far.
* Can I have a free subscription?
**MAYBE.** Ask us @BobPony@outlook.comï»¿
